@node "CAVE RUNNER"
CAVE RUNNER

Get to level 2, then type "SUB B BOYS" (including the spaces).  The screen
will flash blue and:
 'F1' - Gives nine lives.
 'F2' - Sets the timer to 99 - useful for level D.
 'F3' - Jumps to next level.
@endnode
@node "CHAMBER OF THE SCI-FI MUTANT PRIESTESS  (KULT)"
CHAMBER OF THE SCI-FI MUTANT PRIESTESS  (KULT)

You don't have to complete all five Ordeals.  Instead go into the tunnels
(from The Noose) and wait an hour.  Then leave the tunnels and go to the
Master's Eye.  Wait around until the master dies.  Search his body for the
whistle.  Use it and a panel will open up.  Reach inside and grab the egg.
@endnode
