@node "CHARIOTS OF WRAITH"
CHARIOTS OF WRAITH

When instructed to press Fire to start game, instead move the joystick
forward.  You will activate infinite lives.
@endnode
@node "CHARLIE CHIMP"
Hold down the right mouse button while it loads and a message will appear:
"(CHEAT MODE ACTIVE)".  Use the following keys:

          '1' - Baseball bat.      'HELP' - Jump to next level.
          '2' - Golf club.         'I'    - Invulnaribility.
          '3' - Tennis racquet.    'L'    - Get an extra life.
          'R' - Sets time to 24.   'B'    - Collect all BONUS letters.
          'T' - Sets time to 99.   'E'    - Collect all EXTRA letters.
@endnode
@node "CHARLIE CHIMP 2"
Press the left mouse button on the title screen.  During play use the
following keys:

                'HELP' - Skip levels.
                'B'    - Bonus level.
                'E'    - Extra level.
                '1'    - Gives Charlie a baseball bat.
                '2'    - Gives Charlie a hockey stick.
                '3'    - Gives Charlie a tennis raquet.
@endnode
