@node "CHASE HQ"
CHASE HQ

As soon as the title screen disappears start tapping the SPACEBAR at high
speed and continue until loading has finished and the game begins.  Your car
will now have a top speed of over 1,000 km/h.

Hold down the fire button and left mouse button simultaneously and type:
"GROWLER".  Now pressing 'T' during play will reset the clock to 60 seconds.

Before each new level finishes talking hit 'Space' and use a free nitro.
'X' & 'Z' make steering easier.
@endnode
@node "CHASE HQ II"
CHASE HQ II

Hold down 'H' and 'F5' while the game is loading, now all the roadside
obstacles will disappear.

Type "IN A GARDEN IN", then press the following keys for their effects:

   'N' -        Skip Levels
   '1' - '6' -  Jump to corresponding levels
   'W' -        Rocket things
   'T' -        More time (Keep pressing)

If the password doesn't work try "IN A GARDEN" on the title screen or the
above password with no spaces.
@endnode
