@node "CHUCK ROCK"
CHUCK ROCK

When the band are playing during in the title sequence, type the following
(spaces included).  I believe you have to hit 'ESC' before typing.

"ESTRANDO" / "ESTRANO"        Fly mode       ('left shift' toggles on and off)
"MORTIMER"                    Zone select    (use function keys 'F1' - 'F5')
"TURN FRAME"                  Level select   (use number keys '1' - '5')  
"FAST AINT THE WORD"          Infinite energy                        
"UNCLE SAMS"                  Infinite energy   (Press in correct order)
"LIFE IS MY DREAM"            Infinite energy   ('F1' - 'F2' - 'F3' - 'F4' -
"SHE LOVES CLEANING WINDOWS"  Infinite energy    'F5' or the game will crash.)
"ITS FAIRY BOWBELZ"           Infinite energy
@endnode
@node "CHUCKIE EGG 2"
CHUCKIE EGG 2

If you type "ENABLE--F2" into the high score table it will give you infinite
lives.  (Note two minus signs before the "F2").   While holding down 'F2' you
can move into any adjacent room by pushing the joystick in the direction of
that room.
@endnode
@node "CISCO HEAT"
CISCO HEAT

Start the game and type "EGOW", then use the following keys:

                    'T' - For more time.
                    'G' - To abort.
                    'Q' - Show free memory.
                    'N' - Next race.
                    '2' - Go to level 2.
                    '3' - Go to level 3.
                    '4' - Go to level 4.
                    '5' - Go to level 5.
@endnode
@node "CIVILIZATION"
CIVILIZATION

Press 'ALT' and 'R' to randomize the leaders' personalities.  Also on early
versions pressing 'SHIFT' and typing "1234567890t" gives a complete world map.
@endnode
@node "CJ`S ELEPHANT ANTICS"
CJ`S ELEPHANT ANTICS

