@node "CLOWN 'O MANIA"
CLOWN 'O MANIA

During the game press 'HELP' at anytime to gain more jumps and razors, but
the extra jumps and razors will not register until you actuallly jump or
fire.  This can be done as many times as you like.  Click both the
mousebuttons on the titlescreen and push fire.  Now press 'G' for infinite
lives, jumps and shots.
@endnode
@node "CONTINETAL CIRCUS"
CONTINETAL CIRCUS

At the start of the race when the first start light comes on press up on the
joystick and hold it there.  When the second start light appears, pull down
on the joystick and hold it.  Finally when the third green light shows, push
up - you should start off with a faster acceleration.  If this doesn't work
you need faster reactions.
@endnode
@node "COOL CROC TWINS"
COOL CROC TWINS

                             Level Codes:

      6) TRIAX  11) DREAM  16) MUNGO  21) JANKO  26) HENRI  31) DOORS
   
